item.content:encoded: You can see our Hawaii pictures here - http://pics.msn2.net/Categories.aspx?r=1&c=175.  (you'll need to login)  If you have problems viewing the pics, email me and let me know.

wp:comment.wp:comment_content: First off I want to say wonderful blog! I had a quick question which I'd like to ask if you do not mind. I was curious to know how you center yourself and clear your thoughts before writing. I've had a tough time clearing my mind in getting my thoughts out there. I do take pleasure in writing but it just seems like the first 10 to 15 minutes are usually lost just trying to figure out how to begin. Any ideas or tips? Kudos!

item.title: Mike and Sara Giesler
item.dc:creator: mike
item.content:encoded: We flew to Vegas last week and got married!  Many thanks to Neil for planning our surprise wedding!
